OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,Fand strong winds spreading north on
OL,7,FSaturday, very strong for a time
OL,8,Flater. Blustery showers with winds
OL,9,Feasing on Sunday. Mostly dry with
OL,10,Fsunny spells Monday, windier west
OL,11,Fcoast.
